 obtain a surprising result that, for delta-prime shock\nwaves, the multiple bulk graviton exchange series giving the leading\nenergy-dependent contribution to the energy-momentum tensor terminates at the\norder of two graviton exchanges with the nucleus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Feb 2009 20:57:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Feb 2009 14:49:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 May 2009 14:11:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-19"}
