es, are of emerging\nimportance in the quest to find mathematically rigorous solutions of ideal MHD\nforce balance in 3D geometry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2009 08:01:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
